cast.name: 艾伯特·鲁德贝克·林哈特 Albert Rudbeck Lindhardt

introduction: After Ragnarök; forced out of their homes in Asgard, the Norse gods Thor and Freya struggle to adjust to life on earth. A desire to stay immortal leads the gods to cannibalism and near extinction. Running out of godly meat, the constant thought of killing one another, the overdue rent, a pure weirdo of a landlord and an obsessive fanboy - Thor and Freya are finding life on earth to be harder than expected.
